<template>
  <el-table
      :data="tableData"
      :edit-config="{
      trigger: 'dblclick',
      mode: 'cell',
      showIcon: true,
      autoClear: true

    }"
  >
    <el-table-column
        prop="name"
        label="姓名"
        edit-render="input"
    ></el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
        prop="age"
        label="年龄"
    ></el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
        prop="address"
        label="地址"
    ></el-table-column>
  </el-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      tableData: [
        { name: '张三', age: 20, address: '北京市' },
        { name: '李四', age: 30, address: '上海市' },
        { name: '王五', age: 40, address: '广州市' }
      ]
    }
  }
}
</script>
